Jumoke Dada bụ onye ọchụnta ego Naijiria na onye guzobere Taeillo.
Jumoke Dada malitere ọrụ ya dị ka onye na-arụ ọrụ na ụlọ ọrụ dị iche iche na-emepụta ime ụlọ, ụlọ, na ụlọ na-emepụta oche na Naịjirịa

Mgbe ọ dị afọ iri abụọ na isii, Jumoke Dada ghọrọ onye guzobere na onye isi oche nke Taeillo, azụmaahịa ụlọ ahịa e-commerce na Naịjirịa nke mere ka ahụmịhe ndị ahịa dịkwuo mma site n'inye ha ohere ịhụ atụmatụ ụlọ site na eziokwu dị elu na eziokwu mebere eme.
Na Disemba 2022, Jumoke nyere aka nweta $ 2.5 nde maka ịmalite ụlọ ọrụ ya.

N'afọ 2017, ọ natara She Leads Africa Accelerator Award maka azụmaahịa ụmụ nwanyị na-eto eto na-eji teknụzụ eme ihe iji mepụta obodo Africa ka mma. N'afọ 2017, The Tony Elumelu Foundation kpọrọ ya otu n'ime ndị ọchụnta ego 1000 ma nye ya onyinye Diamond Bank Building Entrepreneur Award. N'afọ 2020, e gosipụtara ya na TechCabals Women in Tech na Elle Decoration South Africa 2021.

E gosipụtakwara Jumoke Dada dị ka onye na-emepụta Milestone nke ọdịda 2020 nke Nasdaq Entrepreneurial Center na Nasdaq Tower na New York Times Square. Ọ bụ onye Pritzker Fellow ma soro na '100 Most Inspiring Women in Nigeria' na 2021.

Jumoke Dada abụwokwa ọkà okwu na nzukọ mba dị iche iche, gụnyere Nigerian Energy Forum 2021 na TEDx AjaoEstate 2021. E gosipụtara ya na ajụjụ ọnụ BBC World News na-ekwu maka ihe ịma aka ndị na-eto eto na-eche ihu n'Africa.
